With elinkSmart camera and Alexa skills, you can now interact with your smart camera by voice.

First, select the "Enable Skills" button to link your elinkSmart account and find your camera. Find out more about connecting smart home devices to Alexa on Connected Smart Home Devices: http://amzn.to/291lR7u

To use this skill, you must first create a name for the camera device in the eSmartCam or eSmartLife application. Once you know the device name, you can issue the following command to Alexa:
"Alexa, show the front door camera";
"Alexa, show living room cameras";
"Alexa, show the kitchen camera";
"Alexa, show balcony camera";
"Alexa, stop"
